            <div class="content-box">
                <p>
                    Oodle is a learning management system that takes many of
                    the features of already existing programs and offers them
                    in an easier to use and cleaner manner. Oodle is still
                    currently a work in progress, but more will be added to
                    this section as it is developed.
                </p>
