            <div class="content-box">
                <p>
                    Simple! To become a user of Oodle as either a teacher or a student all you need to do is register and
                    either request to join a class or create your own under the "class" section. From there you
                    will be able to work on assignments, take tests, and see your status as a student.
                </p>
            </div>
