                    set ups steps: <br />
                    1: Click "join slack" on the top navigation bar and follow the instructions to create your account making sure you use the same email you used to register with Oodle.
                    <br />
                    2: Once registered with Slack join a class. You will automatically see the new class in your slack.
                    <br />
                    3: If you are a teacher, to create a slack channel its as easy as clicking "create a slack channel on class creation" and the rest will be automatically handled by Oodle.

